{"tid":469601,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(即刻駁咀) 熱狗完美演繹錢向道理走 財向道理流","createTime":"2017-11-15T12:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T05:38:17.000Z","uid":13825,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12a1b68d8b8a4fece602960e7ec88f2c46763e4f","tid":469601,"uid":13825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">熱狗反骨後成日都講呢句<br />\n錢向道理走 財向道義流<br />\n<br />\n根據以下例子<br />\n<br />\n1. 熱狗台慶得二百人出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 拜神又慳皮燒豬都冇隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 書展啲書又滯銷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 個台燶閪要摺柒左個熱血童子軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. Live stream 又冇錢交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 熱狗仔食KFC都冇錢要上網偷圖老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7. 年宵攤位連維園都冇錢投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我真係覺得天有眼 呢班𨶙樣正正完美演繹 錢向道理走 財向道義流<br />\n<br />\n你班唔講道理 又反骨不仁不義嘅𨶙樣比天收啦 <br />\n<br />\n今次真係蝗天擊殺你班陷家剷喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">熱狗快啲入嚟逐點擊破 即刻駁咀啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"dc74fc825a8db04d86e963c56da3c75f52a2ad4f","tid":469601,"uid":29862,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T17:38:13.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，抺黑"},{"pid":"ba945a1eee35aad1d49244745d2420a0f2f64517","tid":469601,"uid":50984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:59:43.000Z","msg":"但最好笑莫過於佢地已經係過街老鼠仲學人玩清算兼笑myradio係燶閪台話人地台慶搞得肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.